Algorithm 1 : 
Step 1: Find the URL that you want to scrape
Step 2: Inspecting the Page
Step 3: Find the data you want to extract
Step 4: Install required packages in Python IDE
Step 5: Make HTTP request With the help of pakage “Request” 
Step 6: Use “beautifulsoup” to scrap data from selected Website
Step 7: Extract required data from website
Step 8: With the help of Tkinter (GUI) create canvas
Step 9: Add required content and images on canvas
With help of Widgets.
Step 10: After finishing the program, Use “Pyinstaller” to covert python file ‘.py’ to executable ‘.exe’
Step 11: Use NSIS application to create installer for windows
